casebody.head_matter:
Anne L. PRECYTHE, petitioner,
v.
Ernest JOHNSON.
No. 18-852.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 15, 2019.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit for further consideration in light of Bucklew v. Precythe, 587 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 1112, --- L.Ed.2d ---- (2019).
